                    <note>The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient652">London, British Library, BL Oriental 652</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>  ወሀሎ፡ ፩ ብእሲ፡ ውስተ፡ አሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ምስለ፡ ብእሲቱ፡ ወክቡራን፡ ፈድፋደ፡ ወነበሩ፡ ክልኤሆሙ፡
